body:
- Fix for `StreamUtils.tar` there were some problems with un-tarring the resulting object on the GNU tar distribution vs. the BSD tar distribution
- Fix for `LogCopier.Stopwatch`

@liyinan926 can you review?

Changed `gobblin.yarn.job.conf.package.path` to `gobblin.yarn.job.conf.dir`. This parameter now takes in a directory rather than requiring a tarball.

Internally, Gobblin will take the directory and package it into a tarball and submit it as an `ARCHIVE` resource to YARN. The code to make the tarball is in `StreamUtils`.

@liyinan926 can you review?
